<section id="sect-00013">
<title>Adverse Effects and Contraindications</title>
<para id="para-00023">Typical adverse effects include headache, dizziness, nausea, vomiting, abdominal pain, diarrhea, and cough. Contraindications of PPIs include hypersensitivity to PPIs and the drug rilpivirine, an HIV medication.</para>
